When you're fascinated by someone, you can't help but want to know more about them. In today's digital age, it's easier than ever to keep tabs on someone without being too obvious. You can start by looking into their social media profiles. Most people share a lot about their daily lives on these platforms, from what they're eating for breakfast to where they're going on vacation.&#x20;

You can also try searching for them online. You might be able to find articles or interviews they've given, or even just mentions of them in local news or blogs.&#x20;

If you're feeling brave, you could even try striking up a conversation with them in person. This can be a bit more challenging, but it can also be a great way to get a better sense of who they are and what they're interested in.&#x20;
